name: Square Squid Game Baby Yoda
description:
The square version of the squid game baby yoda. There are three versions, Circle, Square and Triangle. Collecting all three will win you the Frontman Baby Yoda on Monday 25th October 2021

There are rules !!! 
Get my notifications on @pixelplanet11 as I may periodically pause things by tweeting "red light" and resume by tweeting "green light."
